==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Forwarding
<hw>For"ward*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of one who
forwards; the act or occupation of transmitting merchandise or other
property for others.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bookbinding)</fld> <def>The process of putting a
book into its cover, and making it ready for the finisher.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>forward-looking</ent>⟦br⟧
